@startuml
[*] --> NotAuthorized
NotAuthorized --> AuthorizeUrlBuilt : teacher sends link
AuthorizeUrlBuilt --> OAuthRedirected : student authorizes identify/guilds.join
OAuthRedirected --> Cancelled : user cancels Discord OAuth
OAuthRedirected --> CallbackReceived : code/state
CallbackReceived --> Rejected : missing code/state or invalid state
CallbackReceived --> TokenExchanged : exchange code
TokenExchanged --> UserFetched : fetch Discord user
UserFetched --> AuthorizationStored : save identity and token
AuthorizationStored --> PopupClosed : postMessage success
Cancelled --> PopupClosed : postMessage cancelled
Rejected --> [*]
PopupClosed --> [*]
@enduml
